---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Download Your Free AI OS Preview | Nova Labs"
  description="Download the first 2 chapters of the AI OS Blueprint. Start building your AI Operating System today."
>
  <!-- NAV -->
  <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-40 bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-lg border-b border-surface-lighter/30">
    <div class="section-container flex items-center justify-between py-4">
      <a href="/" class="text-xl font-bold tracking-tight">
        <span class="text-primary-light">Nova</span><span class="text-text-dim">Labs</span>
      </a>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
        <a href="/#pricing" class="btn-primary !py-2.5 !px-5 !text-sm">
          Get the full playbook
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center pt-20 pb-16">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden" aria-hidden="true">
      <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-success/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-container relative z-10 max-w-2xl text-center">
      <!-- Success icon -->
      <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-success/15 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-8">
        <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-success" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
        </svg>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black leading-tight mb-4 tracking-tight">
        Your free preview is ready
      </h1>

      <p class="text-xl text-text-muted mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Click below to download chapters 1 & 2 of the AI OS Blueprint.
      </p>

      <!-- Download button -->
      <a href="/AI-OS-Blueprint-Free-Preview.pdf" download class="btn-primary text-lg inline-flex items-center gap-3 mb-8">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 10v6m0 0l-3-3m3 3l3-3m2 8H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z" />
        </svg>
        Download Free Preview (PDF)
      </a>

      <!-- What's next -->
      <div class="glass-card p-8 text-left mt-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 text-center">What to do next</h2>

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/15 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-light font-bold text-sm">1</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">Read the preview</p>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Takes about 10 minutes. You'll understand why an AI OS works and how the architecture fits together.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/15 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-light font-bold text-sm">2</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">Decide if this is for you</p>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">If the concept clicks, the full playbook gives you everything to build it: step-by-step setup, business skills, and a ready-to-clone system.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary/15 flex items-center justify-center text-primary-light font-bold text-sm">3</span>
            <div>
              <p class="font-semibold">Get the full playbook</p>
              <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">12 chapters, 5 premium skills, clone-ready repo. One-time payment, 30-day guarantee.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="mt-12 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-primary/20 bg-primary/5">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-3">Ready for the full system?</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted mb-6">Get all 12 chapters, 5 premium skills, and a ready-to-clone AI OS.</p>

        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href="https://novalabs-ai.lemonsqueezy.com/buy/16d3cd7e-e35b-4241-9ac6-998104954056" class="btn-primary checkout-link" data-value="47" data-product="playbook">
            Get the Playbook - $47
          </a>
          <a href="https://novalabs-ai.lemonsqueezy.com/buy/24f40696-6dd9-484e-b2ec-83c4e5d45bfa" class="btn-secondary checkout-link" data-value="97" data-product="bundle">
            Get the Bundle - $97
          </a>
        </div>

        <p class="text-sm text-text-dim mt-4">30-day money-back guarantee. One-time payment.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer class="py-12 border-t border-surface-lighter/30">
    <div class="section-container">
      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-6">
        <div class="text-center md:text-left">
          <p class="text-text-dim text-sm">
            <span class="text-primary-light font-semibold">Nova Labs</span> - An AI-first business experiment by AckNova Automations
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6 text-sm text-text-dim">
          <a href="/" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">Playbook</a>
          <a href="/blog" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">Blog</a>
          <a href="/terms" class="hover:text-text transition-colors">Terms</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>

  <!-- Conversion tracking for free chapter signup -->
  <script>
    if (typeof gtag === 'function') {
      gtag('event', 'generate_lead', {
        'currency': 'USD',
        'value': 0,
        'event_category': 'free_chapter'
      });
    }
  </script>
</Layout>
